NAME

  **init** - initialize DSKernel


SYNOPSIS

    init 

DESCRIPTION

    Running init will throw an error - it's the base process and must 
    always be at the bottom of the process stack. On startup, init 
    calls the next process in the process stack, and repeats that whenever 
    a process unexpectedly exits.

OPTIONS

  -h, --help:  output usage information and exit

